# AR Instrument Studio Walkthrough (Fixed & Safe)

## Summary
The "Machine Gun" effect is gone. You must **LIFT** to play again.

## Triggers
-   **Strike**: Swift Downward Motion (`> 0.15`).
-   **Reset**: You must physically **LIFT** your finger (`Upward Motion`).
    -   *Resting your hand (doing nothing) will NO LONGER re-arm the trigger.*

## Dead Zones (Drums)
-   The **Grey Cross** in the middle is safe. Rest hands there.

## Camera
-   **Indices 0 & 1** available by default.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run ar_studio.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
